"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143168","Department for International Trade","false","2019-09-05","<p>It is expected that Ministers from MOD, DIT and BEIS will attend Defence and Security Equipment International 2019 (DSEI). Last minute diary changes may supersede any arrangements made. Details of the Ministers who attended will be available after 13 September 2019.</p>","Beverley and Holderness","Graham Stuart",,"2019-09-05T11:04:02.693Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143168/answer","Biography information for Graham Stuart","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143168/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143168/answer",,,,,"202","International Trade","International Trade","2019-09-02","Arms Trade: Trade Fairs","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Trade, pursuant to the Answer of 31 July 2019 to Question 280324 on Arms Trade: Trade Fairs, what engagement by Government Ministers will be provided to the Defence and Security Equipment International 2019 arms fair.","false","Biography information for Lyn Brown","West Ham","Lyn Brown","284852"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143169","Ministry of Defence","false","2019-09-05","<p>Various Ministry of Defence assets will be on display during the Defence Security Equipment International exhibition including a number of Navy vessels alongside the quayside and static displays of helicopters, fast jets and vehicles.</p>","Berwick-upon-Tweed","Anne-Marie Trevelyan",,"2019-09-05T16:39:50.947Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143169/answer","Biography information for Anne-Marie Trevelyan","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143169/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143169/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2019-09-02","Arms Trade: Trade Fairs","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, pursuant to the Answer of 31 July 2019 to Question 280324 on Arms Trade: Trade Fairs, what military assets the Government will provide to the Defence and Security Equipment International 2019 arms fair.","false","Biography information for Lyn Brown","West Ham","Lyn Brown","284854"
