"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143474","Department for Transport","false","2019-09-09","<p>Travel Costs are recorded separately for each Minister's office but include travel by officials as well as for the Ministers. To obtain the information in the format requested would be at disproportionate cost as it would require multiple searches of various systems based on the method of travel, how the travel was booked, and which official booked it.</p>","Daventry","Chris Heaton-Harris",,"2019-09-09T12:41:24.927Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143474/answer","Biography information for Chris Heaton-Harris","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143474/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1143474/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2019-09-02","Department for Transport: Travel","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, how much his Department spent on ministerial travel by (a) first class, (b) second class and (c) in total in 2018.","false","Biography information for Ruth Jones","Newport West","Ruth Jones","285145"
